title: Central Statistics Office Ireland, Town Population Statistics by Age, Ireland, 2006
name: Central Statistics Office Ireland, Town Population Statistics by Age, Ireland, 2006
description: This dataset has selected town's population figures for Ireland by age for 2006. These population figures are divided into five year age ranges from 0 to 65 and older. The age ranges are: 0 to 14, 15-24, 25 to 44, 45 to 64, and 65 and older. Percentage figures are also given for each age range out of the total population.
